definitions.definition: Not pretentious or magnificent ; unpretending ; unassuming .
examples: He lives in a humble one-bedroom cottage.

definitions.definition: Having a low opinion of oneself; not proud , arrogant , or assuming ; modest .

main_definition: Not pretentious or magnificent ; unpretending ; unassuming .
secondary_definitions: Having a low opinion of oneself; not proud , arrogant , or assuming ; modest .
